  "title": "🦅 Sales & Recruitment Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong><br />Love talking to people and closing deals? 💬💰 Join Euphoria Organization as a Sales & Recruitment Executive! You’ll be the energy behind both bringing in amazing clients and attracting fresh talent. It’s fast-paced, fun, and full of growth opportunities! 🚀</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Drive sales and hit targets 🎯</p></li><li><p>Recruit and onboard talented individuals</p></li><li><p>Build strong relationships with clients and candidates</p></li><li><p>Brainstorm creative campaigns to boost engagement 💡</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Fresh graduates or early career starters welcome</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and persuasion skills</p></li><li><p>Energetic, motivated, and team-oriented</p></li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Training and mentorship programs</p></li><li><p>Fun team events and activities 🎉</p></li><li><p>Clear career growth path</p></li></ul>",
